{"tid":971014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[防火塗層出水] 隧道天花現滲水痕迹　陳帆話係防火塗層","createTime":"2019-01-06T10:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T13:55:56.000Z","uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e30d940d7749b8cf8065e72981717f8a29bf5bb","tid":971014,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"中環及灣仔繞道將在本月20日通車，今日(6日)所見隧道天花多處地方出現裂痕及疑似滲水，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆指，隧道天花的疑似滲水痕迹是防火塗層，因隧道處於水底及密封，防火及安全設計上有特殊要求，需在隧道頂層噴上30幾毫米的塗層，以確保消防安全。<br />\n<br />\n他指，隧道長達數公里，需分階段噴上塗層，噴塗過程有熱脹冷縮及乾涸情況，而一般水底下隧道都會出現輕微滲水，因石屎並非百分百防水，本身設計有預計此情況出現，已設有排水系統。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，最重要是管理及修理團隊見到相關情況會作跟進，例如灌漿，他認為安全方面沒有問題，並保證：「唔安全係唔會開通」，強調確保符合法規及安全要求才會通車。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於沙中線的評估策略及報告，陳帆指研究及調查工作分三個階段，重申需待完成第二階段，即開鑿最少168點後，若情況不理想，就會開鑿更多探索點。而第三階段會視乎第二階段結果，作實際計算，再決定進行加固或其他工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190106/bkn-20190106163851481-0106_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR2P1RPusLfc_ILJfkRBZgFmMtRsA5bEMYHLt_sDKyZv8GpscBvlk4DtHuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190106%2Fbkn-20190106163851481-0106_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2P1RPusLfc_ILJfkRBZgFmMtRsA5bEMYHLt_sDKyZv8GpscBvlk4DtHuk&d=BtX1zqEsHkrxBPetBXsbF%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=dac15c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190106/bkn-20190106163851481-0106_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR2P1RPusLfc_ILJfkRBZgFmMtRsA5bEMYHLt_sDKyZv8GpscBvlk4DtHuk</a>"},{"pid":"557638e1b17e57093d2ec2402248d34ed7b34f0c","tid":971014,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔撚見三條過海隧道會咁"},{"pid":"4eeca719f8904c7a3b5ce09a119a1c10f61ba0dd","tid":971014,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab47fc86581755498628c5317549f3fdd6eb5c1","tid":971014,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58da08e9299045ad71211df7bdb462a1daf495d","tid":971014,"uid":196552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n一有火警就會裂開<br />\n咁樣可以即時引入自然海水滅火<br />\n係最新既環保滅火技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b6b97412c44d762c876ada1e8fc63a21371c45","tid":971014,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58da08e9299045ad71211df7bdb462a1daf495d","tid":971014,"uid":196552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n一有火警就會裂開<br />\n咁樣可以即時引入自然海水滅火<br />\n係最新既環保滅火技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真正嘅創科"}]}